                )}:1</strong>. The driven gear turns at <strong>${formatNumber(
                  100 / ratio,
                  1
                )}%</strong> of the driver speed, and torque is multiplied by the same factor (ignoring losses).</p>
      `
              );
            } else if (currentMode === "compare") {
              const transA = parseFloat(
